name: evp_md-whirlpool
description:
EVP_MD-WHIRLPOOL - The WHIRLPOOL EVP_MD implementation

DESCRIPTION

Support for computing WHIRLPOOL digests through the EVP_MD API. Identity
This implementation is only available with the legacy provider, and is identified with the name " WHIRLPOOL". Gettable Parameters
This implementation supports the common gettable parameters described in EVP_MD-common(7).

SEE ALSO

provider-digest(7), OSSL_PROVIDER-default(7)
